Enum OperatorType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<OperatorType>

    Serializable, Comparable<OperatorType>

    public enum OperatorType
extends Enum<OperatorType>
    The supported operators by Cubert framework. The boolean field specified if the operator is a TupleOperator or a BlockOperator.
